Title: VALENTINE'S Custom Stuffed Pillow
Body (HTML):
*LIMITED TIME PIECE!* 

Looking to add some style to the interior of someones home? Our Pet Canva Valentine's Custom Pet Pillow is the perfect addition!

Our pillows are 100% made - cut, sewn and printed - right here in the United States. They are machine washable, soft and super durable. 

For the best results, please capture your pet standing or sitting up. Please see our Ultimate Photo Guide for more.

Our Pet Pillow Cover Features:

  • 18"x18"
  • Included: Pillow AND Cover
  • 100% polyester

Title: White Mountains Personalized Pet & Owner Wrapped Canvas
Body (HTML):
Anyone with a passion for mountains and snow will enjoy this personalized canvas! Let us create a one-of-a-kind masterpiece featuring your pet! This is a memory that will last a lifetime!

These Personalized Pet Wrapped Canvases feature a unique design and style. The diverse collection includes a wide variety of original landscapes and scenarios. This exclusive artwork is ideal for featuring you and your pet on any wall of your home. Each ready-to-hang portrait comes with mounting hardware and leveling bumpers. Not to mention, their fade-resistant inks are water and solvent-based, avoiding toxic chemicals. This canvas is the perfect accessory for caring pet-lovers. Let it also be a life-lasting memory of the special bond you have with your furry friend.

  • Includes leveling bumpers to protect your walls
  • Our HP Latex Inks are fade resistant
  • No Chemicals - inks are water and solvent based

Title: Fathers Day Wrapped Canvas
Body (HTML):
These Personalized Family Wrapped Canvases feature a unique design and style. The diverse collection includes a wide variety of original landscapes and scenarios. This exclusive artwork is ideal for featuring you and your pet on any wall of your home. Each ready-to-hang portrait comes with mounting hardware and leveling bumpers. Not to mention, their fade-resistant inks are water and solvent-based, avoiding toxic chemicals. This canvas is the perfect accessory for caring pet-lovers. Let it also be a life-lasting memory of the special bond you have with your furry friend.

  • Ready to hang - mounting hardware comes attached!
  • Includes leveling bumpers to protect your walls

Title: Custom Pet Canva (Limited Edition)
Body (HTML):
*LIMITED TIME - SHANE FOLLOWERS*

Enjoy your PetCanva™ exclusive canvas with a professionally designed piece of art with your fur baby on it! Put it wherever you want, the beauty though is that you can hang on to this sentimental piece of value forever.

For the best results, please capture your pet standing or sitting up. Please see our Ultimate Photo Guide for more.

  • Mounting brackets included - centered on frame
  • Hand glued solid wood stretched bars
  • 1.5" deep

"PetCanva" came from the word "Canvas". We wanted to put a lot of emphasis around how awesome canvases are, especially with a picture of your fur baby printed on it. It's an amazing conversation piece. It's a lifelong piece of value that you can keep with you forever.

Title: Nashville Strong - Personalized Coffee Mug
Body (HTML):
As many of you know, our city of Nashville, TN was devastated by Tornados last week that snuck up in the middle of the night. Homes were flattened, people lost their lives, and our entire way of life was forever changed.

That’s why 100% of the proceeds from this product will go to Nashville Disaster Relief.

We are incredibly grateful for the love the world has already shown.

Together, we will rebuild.  We are #NashvilleStrong.

If you’d like to read more about the Middle Tennessee Emergency Response Fund, go to cfmt.org. 

Shaun (Founder)

Body (HTML):
Driving with distractions can put you and your pup at risk so we built our Dog Seat Belt to keep everyone safe while your pup rides in the car. Built for safety, comfort, convenience, and durability, the Alpha Paw Car Safety Seat Belt is perfect for every trip you take together.

  • Buckles Securely and is IDENTICAL to a Human Car Seat Buckle
  • Solid, All-metal Hardware
  • Quick-Release, Extra Durable Carabiner Clip, 850+ lbs Force Tension
  • Usage Recommendation For Your Dog’s Safety:
    • Place your dog in the back seat of your vehicle
    • Connect the seat belt to a harness instead of a collar

Every time your dog gets in the car they know there’s a chance of fun and adventure at the end of the ride which can make them wiggly and excited! Driving with distractions can put you and your pup at risk so we built our Dog Seat Belt to keep everyone safe while your pup rides in the car.

Built for safety, comfort, convenience, and durability, the Alpha Paw Car Safety Seat Belt is perfect for every trip you take together. The all-metal buckle is built with a human seat belt design, so it buckles in properly and stays secure while driving. The strap is adjustable to fit dogs of all sizes and includes a tangle-free swivel attachment. Built strong and durable with a rock-climbing carabiner made with Aviation Aluminum for a max force of 850+ lbs which allows for a quick release in the case of an emergency.

  3. Adjustable Length for Comfort and Safety
  4. Keeps You and Your Dog Safe While Driving

  6. Solid, All-metal Hardware
